(STAINES &amp; GARCÍA- ROBLEDO 2014, present paper), 
<collectingRegion id="F66E52C5FF85FFC96F72FBB0FEB9574A" box="[274,358,1106,1129]" country="Costa Rica" name="Heredia" pageId="23" pageNumber="374">Heredia</collectingRegion>
